l/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e524524c837a49a29a073d3fc1e84286c7b4f739","tid":1908130,"uid":270532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:00:25.000Z","msg":"幾時可以over Alvin&rsquo;s dead body <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e474000ca92a253ee3e693c4dcc3fae6175bae3","tid":1908130,"uid":94968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:00:45.000Z","msg":"白票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dee2e75fb26ffaa593e4993adec626d398be5ab","tid":1908130,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人手種票唔掂 驚輸到轉電子種票"},{"pid":"7392fe18091e6cf5c70f99b16747cfecfcbff9b6","tid":1908130,"uid":70147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"進攻功能組別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07eebcc481813a8d96ba7b669cd6b6aaf5008e4e","tid":1908130,"uid":195187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"691a2b90d0e5eecfe8043561cb2d19208eceb418","tid":1908130,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:16:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2019/12/20191218/20191218_162754_712.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2019%2F12%2F20191218%2F20191218_162754_712.html&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVpnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=0d4998c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2019/12/20191218/20191218_162754_712.html</a><br />\n<br />\n政府擬於立會選舉示範電子點票<br />\n2019年12月18日<br />\n下載影片| 檢視旁白<br />\n政制及內地事務局局長聶德權表示，政府已就電子點票諮詢立法會政制事務委員會，現時目標是在明年立法會選舉中，在部分人數較少的傳統功能界別作示範。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n聶德權今日在立法會答覆葛珮帆議員提問時說，政府多年來積極研究將選舉不同環節電子化，但任何安排都必須在資訊科技應用、效率、安全風險、私隱保障、公眾信任等多方面取得平衡。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n除了電子點票，選舉電子化的方向也涉及電子發選票和電子投票。聶德權表示，選舉事務處現時安排兩名職員一起發出選票，避免人為錯誤，並確保選舉公平誠實進行。該處正研究用電子系統發票，希望提高發票效率和準確性。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n至於電子投票，政府研究發現，海外國家和地區採用電子投票時都會遇到系統被駭客入侵影響投票結果、電子投票器出現故障令投票受阻、電子投票器購買成本昂貴而使用年期不長、機器變成過時而不再適用等問題。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n聶德權說，從風險管理、資訊保安、成本效益等角度，政府認為要引入電子投票，必須先妥善處理上述問題，社會也須充分討論，作出取捨。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af204a228f209ff50d7b20d50a8e887f1af3a986","tid":1908130,"uid":212519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:06:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1c666166a2baa0f64e598b157d4e59214a32b72","tid":1908130,"uid":83504,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:07:16.000Z","msg":"仲咁落力進攻功能組別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e278add8167e2dc53a125ce2c2e43d6d3dfb2fd2","tid":1908130,"uid":19640,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:08:28.000Z","msg":"唔搶功能組別，之後乜都唔使搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcddf92ef602fa473c4abd12920ecb600376e67b","tid":1908130,"uid":45910,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"68990087b95cfbc68cf96808c1fb2398e952943c","tid":1908130,"uid":29625,"like":174,"dislike":2,"score":172,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"票都唔駛種 直接改票數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:08:31.000Z","msg":"少數派14億票當選無難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6afe546e67e16de44fc635c0198266747999540c","tid":1908130,"uid":174502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:08:56.000Z","msg":"正 d行唔到嘅老人 攤係張床度就可以種票<i